### AI Execution Engine (Rust Backend)

#### [NEW] [src-tauri/src/ai.rs](file:///Users/canerden/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/vibemarketer/src-tauri/src/ai.rs)
- Tauri command `run_skill` that calls Claude Messages API
- Streams response chunks back to the frontend via events
- Handles API key storage in macOS Keychain via Tauri's secure store

#### [NEW] [src-tauri/src/skills.rs](file:///Users/canerden/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/vibemarketer/src-tauri/src/skills.rs)
- Reads bundled SKILL.md files from app resources
- Returns parsed skill metadata to frontend

