### Design System

Rich, premium aesthetics targeting non-technical users:

- **Dark mode by default** with a warm color palette (deep navy `#0f1729`, accent violet `#8b5cf6`)
- **Google Font: Inter** for clean, modern typography
- **Glassmorphism** cards for skill panels
- **Smooth micro-animations** — sidebar hover, button press, output stream fade-in
- **Gradient accents** on phase headers and CTA buttons

#### [NEW] [index.css](file:///Users/canerden/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/vibemarketer/src/index.css)
- Complete design system with CSS custom properties
- Phase color coding (blue for Ideation, green for Building, orange for Launch)
- Component styles for all UI elements

